   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for plum\"><tr><td>plum</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\n<h2>Plum root cuttings (long format)</h2>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>This is data from an experiment to investigate the effect\nof cutting length and planting time on the survival of\nplum root cuttings.\n</p>\n<h3>Variables</h3>\n <ul>\n<li><p> length: Cutting length.  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p> time:\nPlanting time.  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p> survival: Survival status.  </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>count: Number of plants. </p>\n</li></ul>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p>Hand, D.J., Daly, F., Lunn, A.D., McConway, K.J. &amp;\nOstrowski, E. (1994), <em>A Handbook of Small Data\nSets</em>, Chapman &amp; Hall.\n</p>\n<p>Bartlett, M.S. (1935), Contingency table interactions,\n<em>Journal of the Royal Statistical Society\nSupplement</em>, <b>2</b>, 248-252.\n</p>\n<h3>See Also</h3>\n<p>This data frame is in &quot;long&quot; format. See\n<code>plum_wide</code> for the same data in &quot;wide&quot;\nformat.\n</p>\n",
